        "description": "Plan teachers, dentist appointments or even space-shuttle launches. The Scheduler component is highly tunable and engineered ground-up in pure JavaScript. Wrappers are available for React, Angular and Vue.",
        "og_title": "Bryntum Scheduler – The Scheduling Component With Every Feature",
        "og_description": "Plan teachers, dentist appointments or even space-shuttle launches. The Scheduler component is highly tunable and engineered ground-up in pure JavaScript. Wrappers are available for React, Angular and Vue."
