        {
            "id": "block_37b7ed910ff1f314c2115ab92055bf8c",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Feature Set",
            "heading": "Feature-Packed",
            "body_html": "<p>Built on our <a href=\"/products/grid\">Grid component</a>, Bryntum Scheduler picks up many of its capabilities, delivering an interactive Scheduler that supports:</p> <ul> <li>Drag-and-drop event resizing</li> <li>A handy event editor and keyboard navigation</li> <li><a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/export/\">PDF, PNG,</a> <a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/exporttoexcel/\">Excel</a>, <a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/exporttoics/\">ICS</a> and <a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/print/\">print</a> data exports</li> <li><a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/responsive/\">Responsive layout</a></li> <li><a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/dragfromgrid/\">Drag-and-drop event assignment</a></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Built on our Grid component , Bryntum Scheduler picks up many of its capabilities, delivering an interactive Scheduler that supports: Drag-and-drop event resizing A handy event editor and keyboard navigation PDF, PNG, Excel , ICS and print data exports Responsive layout Drag-and-drop event assignment",
