        {
            "id": "block_5ab711fa9026978a2304b954034d59f1",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Performance",
            "heading": "Tuned for Performance",
            "body_html": "<p>The Scheduler blends these techniques to keep load times short and scrolling buttery smooth:</p> <ul> <li>Virtual rendering</li> <li>A lean DOM footprint</li> <li>Heavy element reuse</li> </ul> <p>Bryntum Scheduler keeps that excellent performance at scale and with extras, <a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/paged/\">such as pagination</a>.</p>",
            "body_text": "The Scheduler blends these techniques to keep load times short and scrolling buttery smooth: Virtual rendering A lean DOM footprint Heavy element reuse Bryntum Scheduler keeps that excellent performance at scale and with extras, such as pagination .",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "such as pagination",
                    "href": "/products/scheduler/examples/paged/"
                }
            ],
            "ctas": [],
            "media": [
                {
                    "kind": "image",
                    "src": "../assets/scheduler/scheduler-bigdataset-tree-svalbard-2-scaled.png",
