        {
            "id": "block_35b80aec3b5a6c0ba5ef9594bd1ce23f",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["video-file", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Planning",
            "heading": "Streamlined Planning",
            "body_html": "<p>Bryntum Scheduler comes with event and capacity summaries to back up every decision. Plan and schedule confidently knowing you can:</p> <ul> <li><a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/tree-summary-custom/\">Stop task overallocation</a></li> <li><a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/summary/\">Check the totals</a> across events and other categories</li> <li>View <a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/groupsummary/\">group summaries</a></li> <li>Show <a href=\"/products/scheduler/examples/tree-summary/\">group capacity caps</a></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Bryntum Scheduler comes with event and capacity summaries to back up every decision. Plan and schedule confidently knowing you can: Stop task overallocation Check the totals across events and other categories View group summaries Show group capacity caps",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "Stop task overallocation",
                    "href": "/products/scheduler/examples/tree-summary-custom/"
